snippet.textDisplay: Rather than an attack on your senses, ‘Lal Meri Pat’ creates a sprawling sense of euphoria that lifts the track to new sonic heights. Listening again and again , will make you hypnotized ...Hats off to Coke Studio Pakistan Team
